.\" Man page for Anna Portfolio deployment scripts
.\"
.TH ANNA-PORTFOLIO 1 "February 2026" "Anna Portfolio" "Deployment Manual"
.SH NAME
anna-portfolio \- Anna's portfolio website deployment tools
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B system-hardening.sh
[\fIhostname\fR]

.B deploy.sh
\fIcommand\fR [\fIserver\fR] [\fIenvironment\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Anna Portfolio is a static website deployment system. It includes scripts for
server hardening and automated deployment.
.SH SYSTEM HARDENING SCRIPT
.PP
\fBsystem-hardening.sh\fR secures a fresh Linux server for web hosting.
.PP
\fBUsage:\fR
.IP
sudo ./system-hardening.sh [\fIhostname\fR]
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.IP \fIhostname\fR
Set the server hostname (default: anna-portfolio)
.PP
\fBActions performed:\fR
.IP \(bu 2
Update system packages
.IP \(bu 2
Create 'deploy' user with sudo privileges
.IP \(bu 2
Configure SSH key-only authentication
.IP \(bu 2
Set up UFW firewall (SSH, HTTP, HTTPS)
.IP \(bu 2
Install and configure Fail2Ban
.IP \(bu 2
Enable automatic security updates
.IP \(bu 2
Harden kernel parameters
.PP
\fBNote:\fR Must be run as root or with sudo.
.SH DEPLOYMENT SCRIPT
.PP
\fBdeploy.sh\fR automates deployment of the portfolio to a production server.
.PP
\fBUsage:\fR
.IP
./deploy.sh \fIcommand\fR [\fIserver\fR] [\fIenvironment\fR]
.PP
\fBCommands:\fR
.IP \fBdeploy\fR
Full deployment workflow (default)
.IP \fBstart\fR
Start the web service
.IP \fBstop\fR
Stop the web service
.IP \fBrestart\fR
Restart the web service
.IP \fBstatus\fR
Show deployment status and recent commits
.IP \fBrollback\fR
Revert to previous version
.IP \fBverify\fR
Verify deployment is responding
.IP \fBhelp\fR
Show usage information
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.IP \fIserver\fR
Domain name or IP address (default: localhost)
.IP \fIenvironment\fR
Deployment environment (default: dev)
.PP
\fBExamples:\fR
.IP
Deploy to production:
.B
.br
./deploy.sh deploy anna-portfolio.com prod
.PP
.IP
Check deployment status:
.B
.br
./deploy.sh status
.PP
.IP
Rollback to previous version:
.B
.br
./deploy.sh rollback
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B PORT
Port for web service (default: 8000)
.TP
.B REPO_URL
GitHub repository URL (default: https://github.com/notl0cal/anna-portfolio.git)
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /var/www/anna-portfolio
Default deployment directory
.TP
.I /etc/systemd/system/anna-portfolio.service
Systemd service unit file
.TP
.I /etc/caddy/Caddyfile
Caddy reverse proxy configuration
